<subSubSection lastPageId="38" lastPageNumber="39" pageId="34" pageNumber="35" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="34.[151,1436,1178,1763]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1701,1726]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">Etymology.</emphasis>
Named after the late Ronnie James Dio, according to the senior author the greatest rock singer of all times.
</paragraph>
