<paragraph blockId="38.[151,1437,599,1747]" box="[199,994,1722,1747]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,352,1722,1747]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Distribution.</emphasis>
The species is collected in the Amazonas State in 
<collectingCountry box="[917,989,1722,1747]" name="Brazil" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Brazil</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
